Folder structure
--> src/client: client application
--> src/server: server application

Usage
(1) run server from bin folder (java server/Server) - listens on port 9094
(2) run client from bin folder (java client/Client localhost 9094)
(3) to shutdown server -> press any key on the server terminal
(4) to shutdown client -> close window OR type "bye" after logging in (will have to close window manually)